DocAttribute.Name: PredefinedType
DocAttribute.Documentation: Identifies the predefined type of a earthworks cut elements. This type may associate additional specific property sets.

DocWhereRule.Name: CorrectPredefinedType
DocWhereRule.Documentation: Either the _PredefinedType_ attribute is unset, or the inherited attribute _ObjectType_ shall be provided, if the _PredefinedType_ is set to USERDEFINED.
DocWhereRule.Expression: NOT(EXISTS(PredefinedType)) OR (PredefinedType <> IfcEarthworksCutTypeEnum.USERDEFINED) OR ((PredefinedType = IfcEarthworksCutTypeEnum.USERDEFINED) AND EXISTS (SELF\IfcObject.ObjectType))
